You could wrap your `OverlayModal` in another component (a &#39;Click Muncher&#39;) that prevents any click bubbling:


    const ClickMuncher = ({ children }) =&gt; {
      return &lt;div onClick={e =&gt; e.stopPropagation()}&gt;{children}&lt;/div&gt;;
    };


